Virgin Media Reports Revenue Growth for Half Year of 3.9%

-- B y   J o n a t h a n   B r o w n i n g
-- 
2011-07-27T06:00:00Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-27/virgin-media-reports-revenue-growth-for-half-year-of-3-9-.html
Virgin Media Inc. (VMED)  reported revenue
growth of 3.9 percent for the half-year, with quarterly revenue
growth of 2.2 percent to 986 million pounds, according to a
statement today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
